---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Acme Coffee Roasters — small-batch coffee, Springfield">
  <p class="eyebrow">Roasted Tuesdays · Picked up Saturdays</p>
  <h1>Coffee, roasted Tuesdays.</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    We're a two-person roastery on Maple Street. Single-origin beans, two house
    blends, and a stubborn refusal to roast anything past medium.
  </p>

  <h2>On the bar this week</h2>
  <ul class="card-list">
    <li>
      <strong>Ethiopia · Yirgacheffe</strong>
      <span class="notes">Bright and floral. Lemon zest, bergamot, honey. Washed, 1,900m.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Colombia · Huila</strong>
      <span class="notes">Caramel, milk chocolate, a gentle body. A polite, everyday cup.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>House blend · "Maple"</strong>
      <span class="notes">Cocoa-forward, easy drinker. Pulls a forgiving espresso.</span>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <p>
    Beans go into the roaster Tuesday morning. Orders placed by Friday are ready
    for Saturday pickup, 8–noon. If you want a bag shipped, email us — we ship
    Monday for anything ordered in the prior week.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you run a café or restaurant and want us to roast a house bean for you,
    that's <a href="/wholesale/">wholesale</a>.
  </p>
</Base>
